item.title: CVE-2023-24567|2024-08-02T11:03:18.718Z -- dell -- dell%20networker%2C%20nve
item.description: Dell NetWorker versions 19.5 and earlier contain 'RabbitMQ' version disclosure vulnerability. A NetWorker server user with remote access to NetWorker clients may potentially exploit this vulnerability and may launch target-specific attacks.
